                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/9743" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-1466</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">892 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">智涌质变：华为业财融合的新质跃迁之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Zhiyong Quality Change: Huawei&#39;s New Path to Quality Transition in Business and Finance Integration</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">王珍、狄亚凡</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">三峡大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">华为技术有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">通讯业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务资产部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">14 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新质生产力；业财融合；财务共享；数字化转型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">New quality productivity; Business and finance integration; Financial sharing; Digital transformation</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新质生产力强调科技创新资源的整合，推动战略性新兴产业和未来产业的转型升级。其核心不仅是生产方式的革新，更涵盖管理模式与财务模式的协同创新。本案例聚焦华为在新质生产力背景下业财融合实践，通过早期探索、体系构建、深化融合、智能跃迁四阶段演进，揭示其如何以ERP、财务共享中心、RPA+AI等数字化工具为底座，以财务三支柱模型为支撑，实现业务与财务的深度协同。研究发现，业财融合不仅助力华为在技术封锁下优化营收结构，更通过财务前置决策和风险管控构建核心竞争力。本案例为通信行业提供了“管理创新驱动生产力变革”的范本，印证了业财融合在新质生产力发展中的战略价值。通过本案例的教学与讨论，使学员从华为业财融合的新质跃迁之路中学习和掌握进行业财融合的动因、过程和最终效果，能够分析业财融合对于公司盈利能力及创新效应的影响，从而助力企业提升创新能力，实现长远发展。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The new quality productivity emphasizes the integration of scientific and technological innovation resources, promoting the transformation and upgrading of strategic emerging industries and future industries. Its core not only involves the innovation of production methods but also encompasses the collaborative innovation of management and financial models. This case focuses on Huawei&#39;s practice of business and finance integration under the background of new quality productivity. Through four stages of evolution - early exploration, system construction, deep integration, and intelligent leap - it reveals how Huawei, with digital tools such as ERP, financial shared service centers, and RPA+AI as the foundation and the three-pillar financial model as support, achieves deep collaboration between business and finance. The research finds that business and finance integration not only helps Huawei optimize its revenue structure under technological blockades but also builds core competitiveness through forward-looking financial decision-making and risk management. This case provides a model of &quot;management innovation driving productivity transformation&quot; for the telecommunications industry, confirming the strategic value of business and finance integration in the development of new quality productivity. Through the teaching and discussion of this case, learners can understand and master the driving forces, processes, and ultimate effects of business and finance integration from Huawei&#39;s new quality leap, and be able to analyze the impact of business and finance integration on a company&#39;s profitability and innovation effects, thereby helping enterprises enhance their innovation capabilities and achieve long-term development. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">经营管理人员,本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">改编/二手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">新质生产力；业财融合内涵；业财融合驱动因素；业财融合转型阶段划分类型及特点；业财融合模式</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2025-08</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
